		<h2>Press Release</h2>
		<h3>Strategic alliance for plastic removal and paint stripping</h3>
		<p>Dinamec Systems, LLC of Acworth Georgia, the leading North American manufacturer of gas-heated fluidized sand beds for removing organic substances such as paint, powder coating, and rubber from most all metal alloys, became the exclusive distributor for North America of SCHWING Fluid Technik GmbH of Neukirchen-Vluyn in Germany.</p>
		<p>With over 40 years experience in the international systems business SCHWING is a world-wide known, leading design engineer, manufacturer and operator of electric heated fluidized bed systems as well as vacuum furnaces for premium thermal cleaning processes in the plastics and fiber industry.</p>
		<p>With this agreement in place, Dinamec Systems now provides the North American industry with all advanced thermal cleaning technologies for the removal of polymers, paint and organic contaminations from metal tools and machine parts of any type and size. Whether using pyrolysis, thermal decomposition under vacuum conditions or a thermal conversion process in a fluidized bed, Dinamec Systems offers the right technology for a wide range of industrial cleaning requirements.</p>
		<p>For more information or any service needs please call <strong>1-888-DINAMEC</strong>, send an e-mail to info@dinamecsystems.com or visit www.dinamecsystems.com.</p>
